image.altText: A woman in a TGA shirt is seen standing guard inside a pharmacy

image.altText: A crowd surround a hearse in front of a church.

props.synopsis: A large crowd of mourners at the funeral of opposition leader Alexei Navalny defies government warnings by engaging in a rare public anti-Kremlin demonstration in Moscow.

image.altText: A close up of Penny Wong in glasses observing during a press conference.

props.synopsis: Foreign Minister Penny Wong has asked her department to tell the Israeli ambassador Australia is "horrified" at reports that Israeli troops opened fire on Palestinians waiting for aid in Gaza, killing more than 100.

image.altText: A bald police officer speaks at a podium.

image.altText: Illustration of Luke and Jessie at vigil to celebrate their lives in darlinghurst on friday march 1 2024

image.altText: A middle-aged woman with grey hair.

image.altText: A young man with dark hair, a beard, a suit and glasses walks on the street.

image.altText: Australia bowler Mitchell Starc flinches between New Zealand batters Kane Williamson and Will Young as the stumps are broken.

image.altText: A female footballer wearing gold, running away in celebration, smiling, after scoring

image.altText: Mitch Marsh holds his finger up and runs through after a wicket

image.altText: Peter Dutton speaks in a courtyard at Parliament House

image.altText: An empty supermarket shelf

image.altText: Donuts

image.altText: An animated gif showing an animation of impact on a small asteroid, leaving it slighly deformed

image.altText: Illustration of a smashed piggy bank leaking coins, with a hammer in the foreground.

image.altText: photo of a woman with her hair braided in a pony tail sits on a rise next to a candle in a jar with flowers and a screen behind

image.altText: Anthony Albanese in a grey suit and tie holds up a purple booklet in front of three flags
